	{"x4pointer":" "
	 ,"x4code":{"header":"ERR-T"
	     ,"headerHelp":"Total uncertainty (1-Sigma)"}
	,"x4freetext":[" The error in the gamma-ray yield depended on"
		,"the angle: at backward angles it consisted mainly of"
		,"the statistical error (3-6%) ; at forward angles it"
